    <td class="sponText"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/PCJINDIA?fref=ts"><img align="left" border="0" style="margin-right:10px ; margin-bottom:3px" usemap="#Map" src="/staticpages/mediaintoday/indiatoday/womansummit/2014/images/pcj.gif"></a>      

<p>In a business where it takes the finest to catch the eye, PC Jeweller has won hearts with the Relentless focus on customer satisfaction through unparalleled purity, unmatched designs, complete transparency and the best customer care has made PC Jeweller, North &amp; Central India's reputed jeweller.</p>
<p>The subtle and the royal look that draws everyone's attention is the magic of PCJ. Since 2005 we have added glitter to India with a wide collections of gold and diamond jewellery. </p>

<strong>Vision </strong>
<p>Our vision translated into operational practice, is to develop new designs, products and to serve our clientele beyond expectations. And hence we strive to create value that is attractive, sustainable and growing through intellectually driven proactive strategies.</p>

<strong>The Journey </strong>
<p>Mr. Padam Chand Garg (coming to Delhi from a small village in Haryana) setting-up a small shop in Sadar Bazar in 1981, followed by another in Chandni Chowk.Since then, we have embarked upon a rapid and phenomenal growth.</p>

<p>PC Jeweller values the trust reposed in it by the customers and is committed to uphold it at all costs. Integrity, honesty and absolute transparency have been and continue to be the underlying principles in all our dealings</p>

<p>Over the years, our relationship with the clients has been the most valued asset for us. In an era when profit has become the prime motive, we have continuously endeavored to bring the best of quality, designs and pricing to our customers. </p>

<p>Proactive and timely research, creation of world class jewellery and expert guidance to customers in making right purchasing decisions have made PC Jeweller the name that it has become today. </p>

<p>Today PCJ is competently positioned to capitalize on any opportunity that arises owing to its following organizational attributes that have been cultivated over years. 
Speed: in decision making and execution.</p>

<p><em>Exclusivity:</em>  in strategic selection of complex and intellectually challenging segments.</p>
<p><em>Anticipation:</em> proactive analysis of emerging opportunities; an accurate timing of market entry to capitalize on the first mover advantage.</p>
<p><em>Risk appetite:</em> investment in high reward high risk segments where success can position us among a select few in the world.</p>
<p><em>Empowerment:</em> facilitating experts, leaders and doers to spearhead organizational growth. Putting emphasis on people and processes for lowest attrition rate at senior management level. Reflecting the positive impact of empowerment and leaderships opportunities.</p>
 

<strong>Management</strong>
<p>Behind the expertise of the many lies the acumen of a few because every long journey is begun by visionaries who have the foresight, commitment and dedication to turn it into reality. PC Jeweller, the incredible story of success was conceived by Sh. Padam Chand Garg (Chairman) and Sh. Balrram Garg (Managing Director). </p>

<p><em>Sh. Padam Chand Garg - Chairman &amp; Founder </em>
Sh. Padam Chand Garg is Group Chairman and mentor of the group.Starting with a small shop in Sadar Bazaar, he turned PC Jewellers into one of the fastest growing jewellery chain of stores in North &amp; Central India within a short span of time. </p>

<p>One of the most recognized and respected personalities in the industry with over 35 years of experience in gold and jewellery, he is a person of high ethics, astute business sense and leadership abilities. He has pioneered path breaking concepts in showcasing the glory of creativity in jewellery catering to both traditional and modern tastes.  
Mr. Padan Chand Garg has always aimed at winning customer loyalty through high service and quality standards and believes in building a unique culture based on values and integrity. It is his vision to build an organization everyone can be proud to be associated with.</p>

<p><em>Sh.. Balrram Garg - Managing Director</em>
Sh. Balrram Garg the youngest of the dynamic trio was born in 1970 and is a graduate from Delhi University, he enjoys unconditional trust from all clients in his favour. It is with his initiatives that PCJ jewellery has found new buyers from all over the world. </p>
<p>His official portfolio also includes overseeing books of accounts, statutory requirements, taxation.</p>

<strong>Product range</strong>
<p>PC Jeweller boasts of an incredible range of more than 20000 exclusive designs.Moreover there is a dedicated team for ongoing creation of designs according to taste and need of customers. Besides 100% Hallmarked jewellery and Certified Diamond jewellery, we also provide an alluring ambiance to catch the mood. </p>

<strong>Showrooms</strong>
<p><em>Not just beautiful buildings</em>
We understand that showrooms alone do not make us the best, but the best practices along with beautiful showrooms do. PCJ takes pride in its TQM policy both at product &amp; service level.
The interiors &amp; the exteriors of all PCJ showrooms bear the signature style of PCJ which connects with the audience at once. The stories created inside &amp; outside the showrooms aim at involving the customers into a relationship with jewellery while they make a purchase decision. For the first time, stories were told on in-store brandings that talked about relationships, tradition, love, beauty &amp; jewellery. </p>
<p>The brand has its flagship showroom in Karol Bagh, Delhi and other showrooms spread across Pitampura, Preet Vihar, South Ex, GK-1,Rajouri Garden,Kingsway Camp (Delhi), Ghaziabad,Indirapuram, Noida, Lucknow &amp; Kanpur (UP), Gurgaon, Faridabad, Panchkula,Rohtak (Haryana), Chandigarh, Dehradun, Haridwar (Uttrakhand),Bhopal and Indore (MP), Raipur, Bilaspur(Chhatisgarh), Jodhpur, Pali, Beawar, Ajmer &amp; Bhilwara(Rajasthan), Ludhiana, Amritsar (Punjab). All PCJ showrooms serve a niche clientele with the best of quality assurance and customer care.</p>
<p>One can find contemporary collections and spectacular styles invading all PCJ stores which have opened their doors to connoisseurs of exquisite jewellery across the country. All our stores are a visual delight with ambient lighting and the widest range of bejeweled masterpieces. With the largest assortment of handmade and machine made jewellery in Diamond, gold, kundan and polki on display, every inch of our showrooms is a spectacular sight.</p>



<strong>Brand associations - brand ambassadors, festivals</strong>
<p>Our star-studded showroom launches saw the presence of celebrities like brand ambassador Giselli Monteiro, Sonal Chauhan, Mugdha Godse &amp; Madhur Bhandarkar gracing the occasion. In the past the brand has also been associated with stars like Sridevi and Shilpa Shetty.</p>
 
 
<strong>Brand communication</strong>
<p>Change is the only constant in this world. Our recent Gold Collection campaign re-affirmed PCJ as  "jeweller for generations" that encompasses all age groups. Spreading our wings out of the shield that had housed our initials till now, our new logo with the Triquetra helped the brand to forge new bonds with a younger, more style conscious audience who still looks for trust while buying jewellery. The campaign also launched Giselli Monteiro (Harleen Kaur of Love Aaj Kal fame) as our new brand ambassador.  Playing a role that epitomised undying love and devotion, she also stood as the face of an everlasting relationship, much in tune with PCJ's identity.</p>

<strong>Accolades &amp; awards / certifications</strong>
<p>The mentors of the brand believe that companies that work solely for profits limit their own potential. It is this spirit that has paved our way into the heart of India's Jewellery Business and made us one of the most visible brands in the industry. </p>
<p>However, we do not solely concentrate on making profits but on sustained growth and accomplishing new milestones.</p>

